# ==========================================
# REPOSITORIO GLOBAL - PROYECTO POO
# ==========================================

# --- FRONTEND (React / Node) ---
**/node_modules/
**/npm-debug.log*
**/yarn-debug.log*
**/yarn-error.log*
**/.env
**/.env.local
**/.env.development.local
**/.env.test.local
**/.env.production.local
**/build/
**/dist/

# --- BACKEND (Java / Spring Boot) ---
**/target/
**/*.class
**/*.jar
**/*.war
**/*.ear
**/*.nar
# Configuración local de Maven/Gradle
**/.mvn/
**/build/
**/.gradle/

# --- CONFIGURACIÓN DE IDEs (Editores de código) ---
# IntelliJ IDEA
**/.idea/
**/*.iml
**/*.iws
**/*.ipr
# Visual Studio Code
**/.vscode/
# Archivos de sistema operativo
**/.DS_Store
**/Thumbs.db
